	@if test ! -f $@ && test $(srcdir) != $(builddir) && test -n "$$(find -L $(srcdir)/api.vala -prune ! -newer $(srcdir)/api.c)"; then cp -p $(srcdir)/api.c $(builddir)/api.c; fi
	@if test -f $@; then :; else rm -f $(builddir)/libenchant_@ENCHANT_MAJOR_VERSION@_la_vala.stamp; fi
	@if test -f $@; then :; else \
	  $(MAKE) $(AM_MAKEFLAGS) $(builddir)/libenchant_@ENCHANT_MAJOR_VERSION@_la_vala.stamp; \
	  if test $(builddir) != .; then mv api.c $(builddir)/; fi \
